summary: Small change to Thepal\'s Khajiit texture that makes the nipples more visible and cute pink
descriptionHtml:
I AM NO LONGER SUPPORTING THIS MOD! THERE IS A MOD THAT DOES THE SAME THING AND MUCH MORE HERE: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4686
